P&amp;S, representing it exclusively in Germany, Austria and Switzerland, and
non-exclusively in France.
Last week the UK group said it was in talks with the receivers of a German
company, F Oberdorfer, which might lead to Scapa acquiring the business and
assets of its German, Austrian and US operations.
