In common with other manufacturers, Mitsubishi was unable to bring down
costs quickly enough to compensate for sluggish sales.
The company's heavy machinery division posted a 10 per cent rise in sales to
Y266bn.
However, industrial products and automation equipment sales fell by 9 per
cent to Y242.4bn.
Net profits fell 75.4 per cent to Y6.3bn. Mitsubishi said its net profits
for the year were expected to decline by 19 per cent to Y24bn.
