THE EC may consider retaliatory action against US attempts to reinforce its
trade embargo on Cuba. President Bush approved the Cuban Democracy Act last
weekend. The EC had warned the act might break international trade law. A
Brussels spokesman said: 'Mr Frans Andriessen (trade commissioner) regrets
Mr Bush's decision.'
